## Value, credits and roles

The long-term purpose is to connect useful community activity to transparent value.

Possible outputs:

- AT Credits
- contributor records
- reputation
- role nomination
- member/editor progression
- author or collection community status
- paid or credited work
- internal ledger/reporting entries
- future royalty/transparency reports

The core rule:

> Useful participation should create a system trace.

This trace may later support rewards, trust, roles, transparent accounting and community governance.

